---
title: Sesame-Crumbed Pork & Soy Mayo with Korean Stir-Fried Veggies & Bamboo Shoots
description: This dish is a delectable combo of sesame crumbed pork and bright veggies with an Asian twist; a Korean-style stir-fry sauce.
Finish it off with a dollop of heavenly soy mayo as the perfect addition to round out the meal.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

